creator: FOUND ME
descriptionHtml:
We are all at risk of losing the people, pets and valuables that mean the most to us.

FOUND ME was designed as a global solution to mitigate this risk and provide peace of mind.

We exist to protect everyone and everything important in our customers’ lives.

With FOUND ME, you are connected to everyone and everything you love in case of a loss or emergency via an interactive system of tags, labels, bracelets, and necklaces linked to our APP.

FOUND ME makes it possible for a good samaritan to get in touch with you, a family member or a friend by simply scanning the QR codes on the Interactive tags. The communication is done privately and without requiring to share any personal information such as your name, phone number or address.

WHY WE DO IT
FOUND ME was created to fill an unmet need. We could not find a single solution to protect our belongings, pets and loved ones in a simple, affordable, and reliable way.

Our platform appeals to the very best of humanity, knowing that if it was easier to help someone else, we would all do it.
descriptionShort: In case of emergency or loss, quickly reunite with your Family, Pets & Stuff
